ing: 1 (10 ounce) package Pepperidge FarmÂ® Puff Pastry Shells
2 (12 ounce) jars Campbell'sÂ® Slow Roast Chicken Gravy
1 1/2 cups cooked asparagus cut into 1-inch pieces
1/2 cup shredded Swiss cheese or Cheddar cheese (optional)
des: "Ham and asparagus in a rich gravy are spooned into flaky puff pastry shells and garnished with tangy cheese."
ins:
Bake pastry shells according to pkg. directions.
Mix gravy, asparagus and ham in saucepan. Heat through. Serve in pastry shells. Sprinkle with cheese.
